cs.SY, cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.AI, cs.RO 

This paper presents a technique for controller synthesis for dynamical systems, which is a topic in control theory and robotics. Therefore, cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.RO (Robotics) are the most likely categories. The paper also discusses the use of abstractions and reactive synthesis, which are topics in formal methods and logic, making cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) and cs.PL (Programming Languages) likely categories as well. Finally, the paper uses optimization techniques to improve the performance of the algorithm, which is a topic in artificial intelligence, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a possible category.
